---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About ‚Äî Andrew Giffen" description="AI Product Manager based in Toronto. Building products, shipping experiments, writing what I learn.">
  <section class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="page-label">About</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Hey, I'm Andrew.</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <p class="intro-text">
          I'm a product leader based in Toronto who loves solving messy problems with simple systems. 
          Currently, I'm a Director of Product Management focused on AI products, integrations, and growth.
        </p>
        <p class="intro-text">
          This site is my corner of the internet‚Äîa place to share what I'm building, what I'm learning, 
          and what I've figured out along the way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">What I Do</h2>
        <p>
          I work at the intersection of product strategy, systems thinking, and execution. My sweet spot 
          is taking ambiguous problems‚Äîthe ones where stakeholders aren't sure what they want, where the 
          technical path isn't clear, where multiple teams need to coordinate‚Äîand turning them into shipped work.
        </p>
        <p>
          Areas I focus on: AI-powered products, integration & workflow complexity, onboarding & activation, 
          and building internal tools that make teams more effective.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Fun Facts</h2>
        <ul class="fun-facts">
          <li>
            <span class="fact-emoji">üìö</span>
            <span class="fact-text">I collect vintage paperback books with interesting cover designs. The aesthetic of this site is inspired by them.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="fact-emoji">üõ†Ô∏è</span>
            <span class="fact-text">I taught myself to code so I could build the tools I wished existed. Now I can't stop tinkering.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="fact-emoji">üéß</span>
            <span class="fact-text">I listen to the same three albums on repeat when I need to focus. Currently: Khruangbin.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="fact-emoji">‚òï</span>
            <span class="fact-text">I have strong opinions about pour-over coffee and weak opinions about almost everything else.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="fact-emoji">‚úçÔ∏è</span>
            <span class="fact-text">I write to think. Most of my best ideas started as messy notes that I cleaned up into something shareable.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">How I Work</h2>
        <div class="principles">
          <div class="principle">
            <h3>Start with the problem</h3>
            <p>Before jumping to solutions, I make sure we're solving the right problem. This means talking to users, looking at data, and questioning assumptions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <h3>Ship to learn</h3>
            <p>I'd rather ship something small and learn from it than perfect something large in isolation. Speed of learning beats polish.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <h3>Write it down</h3>
            <p>Clear thinking requires clear writing. I document decisions, write specs, and create artifacts that help the team stay aligned.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <h3>Make it simple</h3>
            <p>Complexity is easy. Simplicity is hard. I look for the simplest solution that solves the problem, even if it means saying no to scope.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          I'm always happy to chat about product, building things, or interesting problems you're working on. 
          Best way to reach me is on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/andrewgiffen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a> 
          or via <a href="mailto:hello@giffen.me">email</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you're looking for consulting help‚Äîwhether that's product strategy, onboarding optimization, 
          or untangling integration complexity‚ÄîI occasionally take on advisory work. 
          <a href="/contact">Let's talk</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: var(--space-10) var(--space-7);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .page-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .about-intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-9);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-9);
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-section p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about-section a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .fun-facts {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .fun-facts li {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--paper-edge);
  }

  .fun-facts li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .fact-emoji {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .fact-text {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .principle {
    background: var(--cream-dark);
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .principle h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .principle p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: var(--space-9) var(--space-5);
    }

    .principles {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>